= Overridden labels

Labels for nodes `big` and `sum` are overridden.


#render-example(
  ```
  digraph {
    rankdir=LR
    node[shape=circle]
    Hmm -> a_0
    Hmm -> big
    a_0 -> "a'" -> big [style="dashed"]
    big -> sum
  }
  ```,
  labels: (
    big: [_some_#text(2em)[ big ]*text*],
    sum: $ sum_(i=0)^n 1 / i $,
  ),
)

